===Collective Noun===
Many collective noun forms are formed from basic nouns by addition of the stem -sto

'''Kirjasto''' Library ''(from '''kirja''', book)''

'''Laivasto''' Fleet ''(from '''laiva''', boat)''

===Variation===

-stö is a front vowel version of -sto according to the rules of vowel harmony

